enhanced_by.reason: The add method directly interacts with FakeValues objects created by the FakeValues.of method.
FakeValuesContext objects are required to create FakeValues objects, which are then added by the add method.
The add method iterates over the paths returned by FakeValues.getPaths() to update the internal map.
The static initialization block uses getEnglishFakeValueGrouping() to pre-populate the fakeValues map, which is directly accessed by the add method.
